              <dd class="mt-2 ml-16 text-base text-gray-500">Get <span class="text-pink-500">$50</span> off our private customized training program using coupon code BLACKFRIDAY when you schedule today!</dd>
              div.py-2.ml-16
                a.btn.paws-btn_primary(href='https://app.acuityscheduling.com/schedule.php?owner=22813151&location=834%20W.%2014%20Mile%20Rd.%2C%20Clawson%2C%20MI%2048017') Schedule Now
